t periods. Ensure good air circulation. Self-seeds readily. Good for tea and culinary use. Zones 3-8, may struggle in hottest humid subtropical summers. Plant in location with afternoon shade.", "availability": "The Seed Collection Australia, international seed suppliers"}, {"name": "''Golden Jubilee'' (A. foeniculum)", "slug": "golden-jubilee-a-foeniculum", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "humid-subtropical", "sort_order": 10, "origin": "Modern cultivar selection", "traits": "75-90cm tall, golden-yellow foliage, upright habit", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "", "growing_notes": "Ornamental selection for humid subtropical climates gardens. Golden foliage needs part shade to prevent burning. Same growing requirements as species. Unique color adds interest.", "availability": "Specialty nurseries, international suppliers"}, {"name": "''Licorice White'' (A. foeniculum)", "slug": "licorice-white-a-foeniculum", "lineage_type": "open_pollinated", "climate_slug": "humid-subtropical", "sort_order": 11, "origin": "Modern white selection", "traits": "75-90cm tall, green foliage, same anise scent", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "", "growing_notes": "White flowers more visible to pollinators. Good humid subtropical climates performance with afternoon shade. Well-drained soil essential.", "availability": "Specialty seed suppliers"}, {"name": "''Alabaster'' (A. foeniculum)", "slug": "alabaster-a-foeniculum", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "humid-subtropical", "sort_order": 12, "origin": "Modern cultivar", "traits": "90cm tall, lighter green foliage, less bushy than species", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "", "growing_notes": "Good for humid subtropical climates with proper care. Lighter foliage may be more heat-sensitive - provide shade.", "availability": "Wisconsin Horticulture suppliers, specialty nurseries"}, {"name": "Agastache rugosa (Korean Mint)", "slug": "agastache-rugosa-korean-mint", "lineage_type": "heirloom", "climate_slug": "humid-subt